
=================================
         BUILD SEQUENCE
=================================

 Login to NTP server
---------------------
Unpack or scp all bulid files
Modify variables file
Run script
# ./ntpserver

 Login to Controller node
--------------------------
Unpack or scp all bulid files
Modify variables file
Run script
# ./controller

 Login to Compute node
-----------------------
Unpack or scp all bulid files
Modify variables file
Run script
# ./compute

 Only required for Open vSwitch not LinuxBridges
-------------------------------------------------
	 Login to Network node  
	-----------------------
	Unpack or scp all bulid files
	Modify variables file
	Run script
	# ./network

 Login to Block node
---------------------
Unpack or scp all bulid files
Modify variables file
Run script
# ./block

 Login to Object node #1
-------------------------
Unpack or scp all bulid files
Modify variables file
Run script
# ./object

 Login to Object node #2
-------------------------
Unpack or scp all bulid files
Modify variables file
Run script
# ./object

 Login to Controller node
--------------------------
Verify build
# ./verify-build

Create a test instance
# ./create-instance

